Draft Release Checklist

1) Update the gallery3 VERSION constant in galler3/modules/gallery/helpers/gallery.php
1a) Look over gallery3/README and touch up anything version specific

2) Tag the release, eg:
   $ git tag 3.0-rc-1
   $ git push --tags

3) Build the release, eg:
   php build.php 3.0-rc-1

4) Publish the release to sf.net
   rsync -avP -e ssh dist/gallery-3.0-rc-1.zip bharat@frs.sourceforge.net:uploads/

5) <insert docs about updating SF.net FRS stuff here>

6) Create a forum topic for the release

7) One final pass over the GMC news story, make sure the download link is correct.

8) Click "publish" on the GMC story

9) Update sf.net, freshmeat.net stories

10) Close the old milestone

